snippet.title: Best VGM 738 - Resident Evil REmake - Safe Haven
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1671 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ghe_tgQvWKQ

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Gamecube / Wii
Resident Evil REmake (2002)
Safe Haven
Misao Senbongi & Makoto Tomozawa
